# Just (`justfile`)

- Prefer **`just <recipe>`** at the repo root over retyping long `cd web && pnpm …` sequences when helping the user run tasks.
- Run **`just`** with no arguments to list recipes.
- **Bootstrap**: `just setup` installs root + `web/` + `test/` with frozen lockfiles (after Corepack enables pnpm `10.33.0`).
- **`just reset`** runs **`docker compose down -v`** (drops named volumes; destructive).
- **`just test`** runs Docker Compose **profile `test`** (**`web-test`** / **`api-node-test`** / **`api-rust-test`** / **`storage-test`**: lint/typecheck, **`node:test`** on web/api-node, **`cargo test`** on api-rust, migrate check).
- Do not duplicate command lists from the `justfile` in rules; **change the `justfile`** when adding a new standard command, then mention the recipe name here only if needed.
